snippet.title: Astral Break  | Southeast Asia Games Onward 2024 Trailer
snippet.description:
Astral Break is a fusion of mech and roguelite action. Experience thrilling "thrust" controls that propel you through dynamic dungeons. Collect diverse modular armors to refine your combat style and experiment with endless synergies to craft your ultimate hero! 

Twitter : x.com/orb_square
Steam : store.steampowered.com/app/3145570/Astral_Break/
